305
00:19:23,458 --> 00:19:24,500
<b>When are you coming?</b>

306
00:19:24,833 --> 00:19:26,666
<b>I have two more important meetings.</b>

307
00:19:26,666 --> 00:19:29,041
<b>Sometimes, tomorrow evening.
Otherwise, day after.</b>

308
00:19:29,708 --> 00:19:30,708
<b>Okay.</b>

309
00:19:31,041 --> 00:19:33,125
<b>Why did you want to
