00:37:28,708 --> 00:37:30,625
<b>CW 1, Seema.</b>

659
00:37:35,375 --> 00:37:36,666
<b>I swear in the name of God...</b>

660
00:37:36,833 --> 00:37:38,750
<b>I shall state only
