<b>on the day of the incident.</b>

1588
01:21:03,750 --> 01:21:06,666
<b>The name of the friend whom
they apparently met over there...</b>

1589
01:21:06,708 --> 01:21:08,000
<b>is Mr. Naveen.</b>

1590
01:21:09,500 --> 01:21:12,041
