- Okay.</b>

1595
01:21:26,750 --> 01:21:29,916
<b>I can't find the CCTV footage
of the hotel anywhere here.</b>

1596
01:21:31,375 --> 01:21:32,375
<b>Sir!</b>

1597
01:21:33,375 --> 01:21:35,125
<b>The Empire Hotel is a three-star-hotel.</b>

