01:21:50,250 --> 01:21:52,291
<b>We did try upon the hotel's instructions,</b>

1602
01:21:52,500 --> 01:21:53,916
<b>but we were
unable to retrieve it.</b>

1603
01:21:54,458 --> 01:21:56,250
<b>Do you have the hard disc with you?</b>

1604
01:21:57,416 --> 01:21:58,458
<b>Yes!</b>

1605
01:22:09,416 --> 01:22:10,958
<b>- What's your name?
- Naveen.</b>

1606
01:22:11,375 --> 01:22:12,458
<b>What do you do, Naveen?</b>

1607
01:22:12,583 --> 01:22:14,125
<b>I run a workshop
for second-hand cars.</b>

1608
01:22:14,250 --> 01:22:15,958
<b>- Where?
- In Muvattupuzha.</b>

1609
01:22:16,875 --> 01:22:18,375
<b>Do you know that young man?</b>

1610
01:22:18,791 --> 01:22:20,291
<b>Yes, I know him.
It's Michael.</b>

1611
01:22:20,333 --> 01:22:21,583
<b>He's my friend.</b>

1612
01:22:21,583 --> 01:22:23,125
<b>We studied together in Mumbai.</b>

1613
01:22:23,125 --> 01:22:25,541
<b>When was the last time
