1631
01:23:05,541 --> 01:23:07,166
<b>and I find that really abnormal.</b>

1632
01:23:08,416 --> 01:23:09,458
<b>You are right.</b>

1633
01:23:10,583 --> 01:23:11,833
<b>That's quite unfortunate.</b>

