2459
02:05:23,750 --> 02:05:25,125
<b>It's a story of courage,</b>

2460
02:05:25,375 --> 02:05:26,375
<b>resilience,</b>

2461
02:05:26,708 --> 02:05:27,833
<b>and justice.</b>

2462
02:05:29,166 --> 02:05:31,416
<b>A young man, comes to this city,</b>

2463
02:05:31,458 --> 02:05:34,125
<b>searching for his friend's house,
to invite him for his wedding.</b>

2464
02:05:34,750 --> 02:05:37,708
<b>To inquire the route
to that friend's place,</b>

2465
02:05:37,958 --> 02:05:39,416
<b>he enters the premises of a house.</b>

2466
02:05:40,833 --> 02:05:44,083
<b>There, he sees a blind girl.</b>

2467
02:05:45,250 --> 02:05:48,791
<b>He is drawn with desire
to that beautiful girl.</b>

2468
02:05:50,375 --> 02:05:53,291
<b>Upon hearing the information
that the girl will be alone at her house</b>

2469
02:05:53,291 --> 02:05:54,875
<b>on the next day,</b>

