02:09:19,583 --> 02:09:20,583
<b>The story is really nice!</b>

2527
02:09:20,875 --> 02:09:22,416
<b>The visuals are even more outstanding.</b>

2528
02:09:22,416 --> 02:09:23,916
<b>If it's a movie,
