2529
02:09:23,958 --> 02:09:25,125
<b>But, this is a court, right?</b>

2530
02:09:25,291 --> 02:09:26,791
<b>Here, it's the evidence that matters.</b>

2531
02:09:28,625 --> 02:09:29,666
<b>Your Honour!</b>

2532
02:09:29,666 --> 02:09:32,375
<b>Verdict of guilt must be based
on the evidence...</b>

2533
02:09:32,416 --> 02:09:34,416
<b>that leaves no room
