2560
02:10:36,125 --> 02:10:39,166
<b>to arrest this young man
and have him on this dock now.</b>

2561
02:10:39,458 --> 02:10:42,041
<b>It's evident that PW 2 Mohammed,
the victim's step-father,</b>

2562
